    {
      "text": "The corridor is quiet now, lit by a single guttering torch. The scuffle brought a spill of rubble down along the wall — and wedged beneath it, something catches the torchlight with a faint glint. The path north leads to the stone hallway.",
      "condition": {
        "flag": "wanderer_defeated",
        "value": true
      }
    },
    {
      "text": "A narrow corridor stretches north toward the stone hallway. A disheveled figure lurches out of the shadows — hollow-eyed, wild with fear. They raise a blade before you can say a word."
